Please provide all information asked for in the new issue template. Without that information, help is not easy to provide.

That said, in your case it seems that you need to run ./configure as outlined in the guide to Installing TensorFlow from Sources.

body:
Please provide all information asked for in the new issue template. Without that information, help is not easy to provide.

That said, in your case it seems that you need to run `./configure` as outlined in the guide to [Installing TensorFlow from Sources](https://www.tensorflow.org/install/install_sources).
